                     <interp inst="t17900526-25-off120" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17900526-25-cd121" type="crimeDate">19th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900526-25-off120 t17900526-25-cd121"></join>, one hundred and eight pounds weight of lead, value 18 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17900526-25-victim282" type="victimName">
                           Samuel 
                           Pole
                        <interp inst="t17900526-25-victim282" type="surname" value="Pole"></interp>
